Taylor Swift Albums

taylor_album.Rd

A data frame listing Taylor Swift's albums.

taylor_album

Format

A data frame with the following columns:

X

Row identifier

album_name

Name of the album

ep

Indicates whether the album is an EP (Extended Play)

album_release

Release date of the album

metacritic_score

Metacritic aggregate score for the album

user_score

User-generated score for the album

Examples

data(taylor_album)
head(taylor_album)
#>   X                          album_name    ep album_release metacritic_score
#> 1 1                        Taylor Swift FALSE    2006-10-24               67
#> 2 2 The Taylor Swift Holiday Collection  TRUE    2007-10-14               NA
#> 3 3                      Beautiful Eyes  TRUE    2008-07-15               NA
#> 4 4                            Fearless FALSE    2008-11-11               73
#> 5 5                           Speak Now FALSE    2010-10-25               77
#> 6 6                                 Red FALSE    2012-10-22               77
#>   user_score
#> 1        8.5
#> 2         NA
#> 3         NA
#> 4        8.4
#> 5        8.6
#> 6        8.5
